description: Dr Syed Waqqar Ali's daughter says "incredibly dedicated" medic "lost his life to his profession"
title: Coronavirus: 'Selfless' Dr Syed Waqqar Ali dies with Covid-19
title_page: Coronavirus: 'Selfless' Dr Syed Waqqar Ali dies with Covid-19 - BBC News
maintext: "There are no words for the battle that we were fighting every day and the battle that my father's been fighting 24/7 for the last three months," she said.
